=== What steps will reproduce the problem? ===
Try one of these:
```scala
  val \u
  val \u2
  val \u22
  val \u222
```

=== What is the expected behavior? ===
After pressing the Return key the cursor should go to the next line waiting for further input, like this:
```scala
scala> val \u2222
     | 
```


=== What do you see instead? ===
The REPL crashes:
```scala
